<document xml:lang="en">
    <header>
        <title>Installing, configuring and switching keyboards in
        Windows 10</title>
    </header>
    <body>
      <section>
        <title>Installation</title>
        <ol>
          <li>Go to the <a
            href="http://divvun.no/no/keyboards/desktopindex.html">Divvun
            keyboard download page</a>, and click on the
            <strong>download link for Windows 10</strong>:
            <p><img src="images/win10/01_download-sme-en.png"
            alt="Download"/></p>
          </li>
          <li><strong>Run</strong> the downloaded installer:
            <p><img src="images/win10/02_run-installer-sme-en.png"
            alt="Run installer"/></p>
          </li>
          <li><strong>Allow</strong> the installer to make changes:
            <p><img src="images/win10/03_allow_changes-sme-en.png"
            alt="Allow changes"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Select installer language:
            <p><img src="images/win10/04_select_inst_lang-sme-en.png"
            alt="Select installer language"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Choose install location, the default is fine:
            <p><img src="images/win10/05_inst_location-sme-en.png"
            alt="Installation location"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Select Start Menu location, the default is fine:
            <p><img src="images/win10/06_start_menu-sme-en.png"
            alt="Start menu"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>You are now ready to install:
            <p><img src="images/win10/07_ready_to_install-sme-en.png"
            alt="Ready to install"/></p>
            <p><img src="images/win10/08_installing-sme-en.png"
            alt="Installing"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>You have to <strong>Restart</strong> after installation to ensure
            the keyboard is working properly:
            <p><img src="images/win10/09_restart-sme-en.png" alt="Restart"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>After the restart, the new keyboard(s) should show up in the
            keyboard menu (if not, continue as described below):
            <p><img src="images/win10/10_keyboard_menu-sme-en.png"
            alt="Keyboard menu"/></p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </section>
      <section>
        <title>Configuration</title>
        <p>The installation done above should automatically have turned on the
        installed keyboards. In case it has not happened, or you want to change
        the configuration, do as follows:</p>
  
        <ol>
          <li>Go to the <strong>Start</strong> menu, and click on
            <strong>Settings</strong>:
            <p><img src="images/win10/start_menu-en.png" alt="Start menu"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Click on <strong>Time &amp; language</strong>:
            <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-en.png" alt="Controll panel"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Click <strong>Add a language</strong>:
            <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-time_and_lang-en.png"
            alt="Add language button" /></p>
          </li>
          <li>Choose <strong>Davvis치megiella</strong> by clicking the name:
            <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-add-sme-en.png"
            alt="Add specific language"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Choose the variant of <strong>Davvis치megiella</strong> you want:
            <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-add-sme-norway-en.png"
            alt="Choose regional variant"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Click <strong>Davvis치megiella</strong> followed by
            <strong>Alternatives</strong>:
            <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-modify-sme-en.png"
            alt="Configure language"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Click <strong>Add Keyboard</strong>:
            <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-add-keyboard-en.png"
            alt="Add keyboard for language"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Choose <strong>Samisk, utvidet Norge</strong>:
            <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-add-sme-extended-norway-en.png"
            alt="Choose keyboard for your language"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Select <strong>Norsk med samisk</strong> and click
            <strong>Remove</strong>:
            <p><img
              src="images/win10/prefs-remove-norw_with_sami-keyboard-en.png"
            alt="Remove the previous keyboard"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Now you have <strong>Davvis치megiella (Norga)</strong> as an
            input language with the keyboard <strong>Samisk, utvidet
            Norge</strong>:
            <p><img src="images/win10/keyboard-done-sme-en.png"
            alt="Language is configured with the correct keyboard"/></p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </section>
      <section>
        <title>Switching keyboards</title>
        <p>
          To switch between the keyboards, and thus switch language, press
          <strong>Windows+space</strong> until your keyboard is activated:
        </p>
        <p><img src="images/win10/switching-keyboards-sme-en.png"
          alt="Switch between keyboards and languages"/></p>
      </section>
    </body>
</document>
